## рҹҡҖ How to Use This Platform

### For Development Team

1. **Setup Development Environment**
   ```bash
   git clone <repo>
   cd socialhub-ai
   cp .env.example .env
   docker-compose up -d
   npm install (in both frontend & backend)
   npm run dev (both terminals)
   ```

2. **Review Architecture**
   - Read `SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md`
